Underworld Inc Series 2 Special: Shadow Kings and Queens
Real world hustlers control the underworld economy. From human trafficking to fake pharma, this dark and seedy world has players on every level. Each vies to take the top spot in their respective niche. Shadow Kings and Queens profit off illegal trades across the globe.
